Morendil    1.5       + 0.5  = 2
Murphy      1.5       + 0.5  = 2
Oerjan      1.5              = 1.5
Proglet     1.5 - 1          = 0.5
Steve       1.5 - 0.5 + 0.5  = 1.5
Order                         13
